### ===========================================================================
### Publish edited appraisal-workflow.json as a NEW version (in-flight-safe)
###
### Run the requests top-to-bottom. Publishing a new version auto-deprecates the
### prior published version but does NOT touch running instances: each instance is
### pinned to its WorkflowDefinitionVersionId and resumes against that schema.
### Only newly started appraisals use the new version.
###
### Do NOT re-POST to /api/workflows/definitions to apply edits — that creates a
### SEPARATE definition (always v1) and collides on the unique (Name, Version) index.
### Versioning stays under the same definitionId via the endpoints below.
### ===========================================================================

@actor = system

### 0. Find the appraisal definition id — copy the "Collateral Appraisal Workflow"
###    id from the response into @definitionId below.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions
X-Dev-Auth: dev-bypass

### >>> paste the id from step 0 here <<<
@definitionId = 019DBA9C-D7D1-7DD9-8B88-A815ACF8EFEA

### 1. Create a new DRAFT version (clones the current published schema; overwritten in step 2)
# @name createDraft
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions/{{definitionId}}/versions
X-Dev-Auth: dev-bypass
Content-Type: application/json

{ "createdBy": "{{actor}}" }

### versionId captured from the create-draft response
@versionId = 019e8456-1f13-74e5-88cd-a1722513492c

### 2. Push the edited appraisal-workflow.json into the draft.
###    The file's top-level "workflowSchema" binds; name/description/category/createdBy are ignored.
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions/{{definitionId}}/versions/{{versionId}}/schema
X-Dev-Auth: dev-bypass
Content-Type: application/json

< ../../Modules/Workflow/Workflow/Workflow/Config/appraisal-workflow.json

### 3. Preview publish impact -> returns breakingChangeHash + safe/unsafe running-instance counts
# @name preview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions/{{definitionId}}/versions/{{versionId}}/publish/preview
X-Dev-Auth: dev-bypass

### confirmed hash captured from the preview response
#@breakingChangeHash = {{preview.response.body.$.breakingChangeHash}}

@breakingChangeHash = 10f8c245cee7405d01fbdfe3d4f4b91721946d341d33c95344c0f1be9fd53b80

### 4. Publish. Prior published version auto-deprecates; in-flight instances are untouched.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions/{{definitionId}}/versions/{{versionId}}/publish
X-Dev-Auth: dev-bypass
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publishedBy": "{{actor}}",
  "confirmedBreakingChangeHash": "{{breakingChangeHash}}"
}

### 5. (OPTIONAL) Inspect version history — confirm new version Published, old Deprecated
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions/{{definitionId}}/versions
X-Dev-Auth: dev-bypass
